trans-unit.source: Provides a serializable type of endpoint address that is WS-Addressing V1 compliant and that enables it to be exposed as part of the service contract.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder en serialiserbar type Endepunktadressen som WS-adressering V1 kompatible og som gjør det mulig å vises som en del av servicekontrakten.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddress> is not serializable nor is it tied to a particular version of the WS-Addressing specification.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddress>er serialiserbare eller knyttet til en bestemt versjon av WS-adressering-spesifikasjonen.</xref:System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddress>

trans-unit.source: This class provides a WS-Addressing V1 compliant wrapper for the <xref:System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddress> that is serializable (implements the <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.ISerializable> interface) and bound to the WS-Addressing V1 wire format.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen gir en WS-adressering V1 kompatible tekstbryting for den <xref:System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddress>som er serialiserbare (implementerer den <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.ISerializable>grensesnittet) og bundet til WS-adressering V1 wire-formatet.</xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.ISerializable> </xref:System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddress>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddress10.FromEndpointAddress%28System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddress%29> method does the wrapping and the <xref:System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddress10.ToEndpointAddress%2A> method does the unwrapping, allowing the recovery of the endpoint address after it is serialized on the wire.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddress10.FromEndpointAddress%28System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddress%29>metoden har wrapping og <xref:System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddress10.ToEndpointAddress%2A>metoden har den unwrapping, slik at gjenoppretting av Endepunktsadressen når den er serialisert på nettet.</xref:System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddress10.ToEndpointAddress%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddress10.FromEndpointAddress%28System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddress%29>

trans-unit.source: [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] also supplies a class that provides a serializable type, <xref:System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddressAugust2004>, which is WS-Addressing August 2004 compliant for legacy purposes.
trans-unit.target: [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]leverer også en klasse som gir en serialiserbar type <xref:System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddressAugust2004>, som er WS-adressering August 2004 kompatible eldre formålene.</xref:System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddressAugust2004>
